data.description: Attention Investors & First Time Home Buyers. Here is your opportunity to own this 1.5 story, 3 Bedroom, 1 Bathroom home with basement and 2 car garage with a fully fenced in back yard. Home is being SOLD AS IS and seller will not do any repairs. However, buyers are welcome to have inspections done. This home may qualify for FHA, VA & Conventional loan programs.  Contact the list agent for details. Buyer and/or Buyer's Agent to verify square footage and all utilities.
